Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:33.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}見つめあうさざ波は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:39.70,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}君と交わすメッセ一ジ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:45.80,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}この青い海でつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:51.10,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}光の道標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:57.40,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}優しいひとに出会えてるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:02.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}今、笑えてるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:08.60,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}{\pos(505,5)\fs32}め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:08.60,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}星明かり凪ぐ淋し気な瞳に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:13.80,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}輝きを満たして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:19.15,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}I'm close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:25.30,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}いつも傍にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:30.46,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}{\pos(55,5)\fs32}あ  す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:30.46,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}明日が見えない夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:36.55,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}心で呼びかけてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:41.70,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}Please, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:48.00,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}どうかあきらめずに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:58.00,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}いつか手を取りあえる朝まで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:08.50,ED JP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:33.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}目光相汇的涟漪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:39.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}是和你之间的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:45.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}在这片蔚蓝之海上联系着的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:51.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}光之信标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:57.40,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}是否遇到了温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:02.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}现在的我有在笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:08.60,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}繁星照耀的寂寞眼瞳里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:13.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}洒满了光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:19.15,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}I'm close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:25.30,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:30.46,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}即便是看不见明天的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:36.55,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}也会用心灵呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:41.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}Please,stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:48.00,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}请务必不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:58.00,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}直到能够牵手迎接日出的早晨
